12. The real win condition

The true win is not making them look foolish.

The true win is one of these:
	•	you remain uncaptured
	•	the better standard becomes visible
	•	the conversation moves toward reality
	•	bad premises lose authority
	•	pressure fails to force false agreement

That is a mature system.

